---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Privacy Policy" 
      description="Last updated: 8/20/25"
    />
    
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose dark:prose-invert prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:font-semibold prose-a:text-primary-600 dark:prose-a:text-primary-400 prose-img:rounded-lg">
          <p class="lead">
            SnapSites LLC (“Company,” “we,” “our,” or “us”) values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our Service (“Service”).
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <br>
          
          <h3>Personal Data</h3>
          <p>
            We do not actively collect personal data from visitors except when you voluntarily provide it through our contact form. This may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
            <li><p>Name</p></li>
            <li><p>Email address</p></li>
            <li><p>Any additional details you provide in your message</p></li>
          </ul>
          <br>
          
          <h3>Analytics and Usage Data</h3>
          <p>
            We use Netlify Analytics to measure website traffic and usage. Netlify Analytics does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information. We only see aggregated, anonymous data such as page views, visit counts, and referrer information.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We only use the information you provide to: Respond to inquiries submitted through the contact form; Provide customer support and resolve issues. We do not sell, rent, or trade your data to third parties.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Payment Processing</h2>
          <p>
            All payments are securely processed through Stripe. We do not collect, store, or have access to your payment information. Stripe may collect certain personal or financial data as required to process your payment in accordance with their own Privacy Policy.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            Our Service may include links or integrations with third-party services (such as Stripe). Your use of these services is governed by their respective privacy policies.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Contact form submissions are retained only as long as necessary to respond to your request. We may keep minimal records for administrative or legal compliance purposes.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
          </p>
          <br>
          
          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">contact us</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout> 
